overview: Cadence Lux, her girlfriends...and all their other girlfriends have got drama to the highest degree! They're gonna solve it the only way they know how - with lots of passionate girl-on-girl sex. Featuring Cecilia Lion, Serene Siren, Vina Sky, Jenna Fox, Bunny Colby and Ember Snow.
tagline: Tainted passion turns into obsessed lust. Drama to the highest degree.
title: Lesbian PsychoDramas 34
